      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:23:2",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ الْمَرْأَتَيْنِ تُوجَدَانِ فِي لِحَافٍ وَاحِدٍ قَالَ تُجْلَدُ كُلُّ وَاحِدٍ مِنْهُمَا مِائَةَ جَلْدَةٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Usman Bin Isa, from Sama’at Bin Mahran who said, ",
          "‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about the two women, both found in one quilt. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Each one of them should be whipped one hundred lashes’."
        ]
      }
